headline: Paycom Achieves Background Screening Credentialing Council Accreditation
summary: RALEIGH, N.C., April 21, 2025--The Professional Background Screening Association (PBSA®) Background Screening Credentialing Council (BSCC) announced today that Paycom has successfully demonstrated compliance with the Background Screening Organization Accreditation Program (BSOAP) and will now be formally recognized as BSCC-Accredited to the US Employment Screening Standard.
